課程目標 Objectives




　　　　　　　　
This yearly course aims to familiarize students with a variety of paragraph writing tecchniques while reviewing their art of styling sentences. 




授課方式 Teaching methods




　　　　　　　　
Lecturing; Group Presetation; Panel Dicussion; Peer Editoring




評分方式﹝評分標準及比例﹞Evaluation (Criteria and ratio)等第制單科成績對照表 letter grading reference





　　　　　　　　
Assignments, In-Class Practice, Regular Attendance (80%); Group Presentation (10%); Self-Evaluation (10%) 




